event.title: best makeup artist in kerala
event.description: Makeup is a fancying world which is glamorous and at the same time artistic. Be it a wedding or films makeup artists are of great demand . -No wonder, the best makeup artist in Kerala is the most best wedding makeup in kerala searched query.-Everybody wants to find out who can give the best look based on their knowledge and experience. However, although Kerala is small state in the southern tip of India way far away from the fashion capital of India, it is blessed with a number of gifted makeup artists.
